text: The 69th Rifle Corps was a corps of the Soviet Red Army. It was part of the 20th Army. It took part in the Great Patriotic War. == Organization == * 73rd Rifle Division * 229th Rifle Division * 233rd Rifle Division == Commanders == * Major General Yevdokim Mogilovchik * Major General Timofey Kruglyakov (July - November 1943) Category:Rifle corps of the Soviet Union
title: 69th Rifle Corps
